Chapter 3 — Article System & Editorial Standards
3.1 Purpose

Every Embedded Nerd article must be a complete learning resource.

The reader should not need to search for additional tutorials to complete the project.

Each article should teach:

the theory
the hardware
the wiring
the code
the expected output
troubleshooting
practical applications

A complete tutorial always has greater educational value than a short tutorial.

