⭐ 3.27 Embedded Nerd Gold Standard

Every article published on Embedded Nerd should answer every question a beginner is likely to ask about the topic. If, after reading the tutorial, a user still needs to search for basic information elsewhere, the article is not yet complete.

The objective is not to create another tutorial.

The objective is to create the tutorial that readers bookmark, recommend and return to because it is the most complete, accurate and practical resource available.


